{
  "texts": [
    "Given that GPT-4o is the most recent series of GPT-4 that naturally supports multimodal capabilities, we adopted GPT-4o as the tested LLMs.",
    "Specifically, we used \"GPT-4o-2024-05-13\"foot_4 as the targeted model through OpenAI Azure's API 5.",
    "For the few-shot experiment, we tested the 1-shot learning scenario to examine the capability of multi-model LLMs with limited information provided.",
    "In each repeated trial, we randomly selected one sample from the corresponding dataset to act as the 1-shot sample.",
    "This strategy mitigates the bias of selecting samples."
  ]
}